Users: adults, men, women, girls, boys, children, the elderly, teenagers Multipurpose: fall napkins, christmas napkins, wedding napkins, party napkins, hotel napkins, restaurant napkins, banquet table napkins, cocktail napkins,thanksgiving napkins, halloween napkins, birthday napkins bridal shower napkins, baby shower napkins, dessert napkins, custom napkins, baby shower napkins for girl, fall napkins cloth, decorative napkins, funny cocktail napkins, wedding cocktail napkins,table napkins, napkins for wedding reception. Perfect Gifts: Thanksgiving Gifts, Halloween Gifts, Christmas Gifts, New Year's Gifts, Valentine's Day Gifts, St. Patrick's Day Gifts, Mother's Day Gifts, Father's Day Gifts, Birthday Gifts, Wedding Gifts, Housewarming Gifts, Engagement Gifts, etc. How to Fold a Napkin? Silverware Pouch 1,Make a rectangle by lifting the top down and lining the edges up. 2,Fold the right edges over to the left side to make a small square. 3,Flip the napkin over so the open corner is on the top left. 4,Bring the top layer of fabric down from the top left to the bottom right. 5,Flip the napkin again so the opening is on the top right. 6,Fold 1/3 of the fabric on the right side over to the middle of the napkin. 7,Bring the left 1/3 over the center so the folded sides overlap. 8,Flip the napkin over and insert your silverware in the pouch.
